"""Stage 1 risk scorer — cheap filter that runs on ALL signals.

Five scoring components (all local / free):
  1. Keyword match       — 500-term lexicon across 15 signal types against title + text
  2. Entity fuzzy match  — rapidfuzz ratio of NER entities vs KYC name
  3. Sanctions lookup    — OpenSanctions API exact match (deterministic, $0)
  4. Embedding cosine    — sentence-transformers vs KYC baseline business model
  5. Rule-based delta    — CEO name, jurisdiction, legal form in article text

Every signal is written to the audit log regardless of score.
Articles with risk_score >= ESCALATION_THRESHOLD are flagged for Stage 2.

Usage:
    python stage1_scorer.py --company-id CUST-002
    python stage1_scorer.py --company-id CUST-002 --no-embeddings  # faster, skip step 4
"""

